column2: Because schools are shut down, I’m doing 1-on-1 phone calls with my students. Today, I talked with 12 students in 2 hours 😖 it’s hard, but one of my students said “teacher, 코로나 조심 하세요” (be careful of corona) and I just 😭 I love them so much!

“My headache was killing me,” 83-yr-old Park recollected on her battle with #Covid19. Initially she had no fever, no cough. She is cured after 2-wk treatment. But she said she prayed to God that she would die bc she felt such deep guilt over the pain 1/

코로나 바이라스 때문에 코로나 맥주도 큰 타격을 입고있다고한다. 한조사기관에 따르면 맥주를 마시는 미국인의 38%가 현재 어떤 상황에서도 코로나를 구매하지 않을 것으로 답변했으며, 16%는 코로나 맥주가 코로나 바이러스와 관련이 있는지에 대해 혼란스러워했다고 🤣 https://www.usatoday.com/story/money/food/2020/02/27/coronavirus-corona-beer-name-association-outbreak-fears/4894784002/
